{"tid":291101,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打用緊Philip Hue 隻變色燈膽","createTime":"2017-06-20T09:48:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T13:15:41.000Z","uid":50878,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1511563a79d234811e703b17662eef92083a8471","tid":291101,"uid":50878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T09:48:30.000Z","msg":"想用黎做天花燈膽<br />\n<br />\n而家間房好傳統咁得一個白色慳電膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屎忽痕想整個識變色既<br />\n<br />\n但都講求實用性，夠唔夠光<br />\n<br />\n睇過Philip Hue 隻led 燈應該係普通慳電膽既三分一光度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無巴打用過覺得點？ 可唔可以買個吊架將3個膽加埋一齊用等佢光d?<br />\n<br />\n同問呢隻燈膽邊度買最方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n感謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797f055b55e76f6de7acb1333ce51f0dd57e966a","tid":291101,"uid":33176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T10:29:23.000Z","msg":"會唔會變到雞竇咁"},{"pid":"c4f8e25931a4065a03b2fac414ddc7b582ab6955","tid":291101,"uid":45635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T10:31:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會變到雞竇咁</blockquote><br />\n會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n生巴巴，斯巴巴"},{"pid":"8edaa13c841a1b372f5497fb2ccf26d65088429b","tid":291101,"uid":50878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T10:34:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會唔會變到雞竇咁</blockquote><br />\n會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n生巴巴，斯巴巴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nset 做打丁模式， 然後同siri 講我要打丁就轉色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2850f82a841927ed433010e954e01e590ffeed","tid":291101,"uid":17705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T10:51:52.000Z","msg":"勁正， 而家用喂sir